div1.p: United States of America, Western DISTRICT OF Washington } SS:
I hereby certify and return that I served the annexed Writ of Habeas Corpus on the therein-named Henry M. White, Commissioner of Immigration
by handing to and leaving a true and correct copy thereof with him personally at Seattle in said District on the 16th day of July, A.D. 1915
United States District Court. Western DISTRICT OF WASHINGTON.
In the Matter of the Application of Chin Sheung Wing For Writ of Habeas Corpus.

Let the within Writ issue.
U.S. District Judge.
FILED IN THE U.S. District Court, Western Dist. of Washington, NORTHERN DIVISION JUL 20 1915 FRANK L. CROSBY, Clerk, By Emy Deputy 2x
